{"id":"318612120_Structured_Robust_Control_Against_Mixed_Uncertainty","abstract":"We present new approaches to designing structured controllers, which are robust in the presence of mixed real parametric and complex dynamic uncertainty. As the synthesis of such controllers is inherently NP-hard, we discuss inner and outer relaxation techniques, which make this problem amenable to computations. Our relaxation methods are positively evaluated and compared on the basis of a rich test set and for a challenging missile pilot design problem.","authors":["Raquel Stella da Silva de Aguiar","Pierre Apkarian","Dominikus Noll"],"meta":["July 2017Control Systems Technology, IEEE Transactions on PP(99):1-11","DOI:10.1109/TCST.2017.2723864"],"references":["327671185_Nonsmooth_H_Synthesis","299356308_Branch_and_bound_algorithm_with_applications_to_robust_stability","283473007_Nonsmooth_Bundle_Trust-region_Algorithm_with_Applications_to_Robust_Stability","271526591_Robustness_in_the_Presence_of_Mixed_Parametric_Uncertainty_and_Unmodeled_Dynamics","264002091_Multi-Model_Multi-Objective_Tuning_of_Fixed-Structure_Controllers","262416444_Parametric_Robust_Structured_Control_Design","228979427_Nonsmooth_Optimization_for_Multidisk_H_Synthesis","224381630_Robust_Multi-Objective_Control_Toolbox","3032435_The_Scenario_Approach_to_Robust_Control_Design","268494918_On_a_Certain_Linear_Fractional_Transformation","258395264_RealComplex_K_m-Synthesis_without_Curve_Fitting","245430891_Application_of_Popov_controller_synthesis_to_benchmark_problems_with_real_parameter_uncertainty","235100914_Parametric_Uncertainty_Reduction_in_Robust_Multivariable_Control","232347282_Linear_Matrix_Inequalities_in_robustness_analysis_with_multipliers","227322745_Multi-Model_Approaches_to_Robust_Control_System_Design","225075788_Robust_and_Optimal_Control","224660947_Stabilization_of_LFT_systems","222462713_Doyle_JC_The_complex_structured_singular_value_Automatica_29_71-109","3650390_Advances_in_the_computation_of_th